ults can significantly differ based on grill types (charcoal vs. gas), which warrants further exploration of equipment choices.\n- The balance of flavor and nutrition in accompaniments raises questions about dietary considerations, offering a deeper context for healthy eating in conjunction with grilled dishes.\n\n### Keywords\nGrilled, Chicken, Flavor, Marination, Techniques, Temperature, Moisture, Accompaniments",
